Setting up our first home has been such a special experience…
And discovering spaces like @tharartsandfurniture made it even more beautiful.

From intricate brass idols to soulful decor pieces, everything felt warm, rooted, and so us. I picked a few pieces that instantly added character to our new space — and honestly, I can’t wait to see how it all comes together.

If you’re someone who loves a mix of tradition, design, and pieces that actually mean something — this place is a must-visit.

Grateful for moments like this. Grateful for a home that’s starting to feel like ours.
